Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:15.24,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,Training with Rin-san, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:17.07,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,What's she like anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:21.33,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,She drew out Hayato and Prontea,\Nand taught them how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:28.96,sign_512_6__2_The_Black__So,Ep Title,0,0,0,,#2\NThe\NBlack\N South
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:26.10,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,She's also a survivor of the Idaten who \Nbattled the demons 800 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:28.96,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,The only living being to truly understand\N the demonic involvement of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:32.49,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,She's the strongest Idaten\N in current existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:36.22,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,If we're going to learn how to fight, \Nshe's the best person to turn to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:40.72,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Plus, at the moment, it's dangerous to be \Napart from either her or Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:44.19,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,According to Hayato, \Nthat doctor was a robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:46.29,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,We can assume whoever was controlling it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:49.23,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,is now in possession of all the data \Nit collected during our battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:53.90,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Suppose they have a minion even more \Npowerful than that demonic beast,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:55.24,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,and it were to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:56.80,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,We'd be done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:59.39,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,If we stick with Hayato and Rin-san \Nunder the premise of training,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:01.49,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,we can probably avoid getting done in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:02.92,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,Probably?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:07.32,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Well, the plan doesn't preclude the \Npossibly of getting killed by Rin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:12.25,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm not thrilled about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:14.77,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{\an8}I used to train alongside Hayato,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.61,0:01:17.67,Italics,Paula,0,0,0,,At the time, I thought to myself,\N "What's the big deal?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.77,0:01:16.77,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{\an8}and as embarrassing as it is to admit,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:19.63,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{\an8}it was so harsh that\N I turned tail after three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:21.01,Italics,Paula,0,0,0,,"Why is Ysley exaggerating so much?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:21.01,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{\an8}I haven't seen Rin-san since.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.02,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Time to die, you old—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:01:59.72,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Just as brutal as I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.63,0:02:15.52,Show_Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(4409,938)\fscy140}The Idaten {\c&H21FCFB&}Dei{\c&H2601D4&}ties\N{\fs24\c&H19F7D8&\i0\3c&H3E679B&\fscy100}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hKn{\c&HD6E1F9&}ow {\c&H19F7D8&}On{\c&HD6E1F9&}ly {\c&H19F7D8&}Pe{\c&HD6E1F9&}ac{\c&H19F7D8&}e
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:31.98,Show_Title,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H6C171A&}The Idaten {\c&H21FCFB&}Dei{\c&H2601D4&}ties\N{\c&H3FCC78&\fs24\i0\fscy100}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hKn{\c&HC29AE7&}ow {\c&H3FCC78&}On{\c&HC29AE7&}ly {\c&H3FCC78&}Pe{\c&HC29AE7&}ac{\c&H3FCC78&}e
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:42.51,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,What... What was that?! You call that training?\N It looked like a beating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:47.99,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Well, er, theoretically. \NIt's the proper way to train an Idaten, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.82,Italics,Ys,0,0,0,,The problem is that Rin-san \Ndoesn't understand the theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:53.39,Italics,Ys,0,0,0,,She's just doing what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.08,Italics,Ys,0,0,0,,And that's terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:04:00.09,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,Come on, Ysley. Wouldn't it be safer \Nto go learn from Prontea-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:03.51,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,She vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:10.43,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Well, well... We meet again, Ysley.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:14.69,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,It's been, what, fifty years? \NAnd you have the nerve to show up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.78,Italics,Paula,0,0,0,,What's with this unbelievable bloodlust?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:24.15,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,Shit. She's even angrier than I anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:26.59,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,The wrong answer here means death,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:29.27,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,and no excuse will be enough \Nto make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.41,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,That being the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.62,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,I have only one option!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:35.08,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,Rin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:39.53,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,I can't deny that I ran \Nfrom your training once before,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:42.67,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,and I know how presumptuous \Nit may seem after all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.38,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,but please teach me how to fight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.33,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,Ysley took the direct approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.39,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\an8\b1\fs30\shad0\bord0\c&H000100&\pos(306.857,86.571)}D\NI\NR\NE\NC\NT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:51.14,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,He straightforwardly, without pretense,\N asked for what he wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:51.14,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\an8\b1\fs40\shad0\bord0\c&H000100&\pos(231.428,50.571)}D\NI\NR\NE\NC\NT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:54.84,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,which effectively served\Nto mask his true intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.41,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b1\bord0\c&H030100&\4c&HA60E97&\pos(137,32)}True Intentions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:55.52,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b1\bord0\c&H030100&\4c&HA60E97&\pos(509,133)}Mask
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.52,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,And it was super effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:03.90,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,To Rin, who was driven by her\Nsense of duty to fight demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:07.94,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,an Idaten who shirked his training \Nin order to learn in the human world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:11.41,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,was essentially the same as a shut-in \Nwho did nothing but play porn games all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:14.66,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,But when Ysley spoke, it was as if
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.58,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,that sort of fail-son suddenly \Nput on a business suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.45,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry for everything \NI put you through!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:23.11,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Starting today, I'm going to turn \Nover a new leaf and look for a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:27.68,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,And the degree to which this affected Rin\Nwas not unlike that of a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:33.01,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,I see, I see! So you've \Nfinally realized your duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:36.81,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Oh, Grandfather! I've never been happier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:42.19,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Now then, Ysley, who's the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.93,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Oh, right. This is a new Idaten...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.93,0:05:47.07,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,My name is Paula. It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.57,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Really? Did you draw her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.16,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Or was it Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:55.08,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I was drawn out by Prontea-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:58.33,Caption base,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1230,1)}"Drawing Out"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:58.33,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,Idaten are naturally occurring entities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:02.20,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,If they are left alone, they will still \Nmanifest within a few centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:04.13,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,But with the intervention of another Idaten,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:07.34,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,they can be drawn out in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:11.25,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,Those drawn out in this fashion often take
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.93,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,the Idaten responsible as their master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.10,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,This is why Rin, \Nwho spends nearly all her time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.40,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,where the demons have been sealed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:21.37,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,will occasionally travel \Nacross the world with Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:25.90,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,She means to find and draw out\Nnew Idaten to join her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.71,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Oh, Prontea, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:29.26,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,That takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:32.76,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,It took me 200 years to\N train him into shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:37.62,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Of all my students, he's the only one \NI'd say can stand on his own two feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:41.29,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,So, are you here to train, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:43.32,Italics,Paula,0,0,0,,I still regret it to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:46.05,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,Well, that's what I was thinking of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:51.30,Italics,Paula,0,0,0,,Why didn't I just say no\Nand run away back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:53.93,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.40,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Come at me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:06:59.66,Italics,Paula,0,0,0,,What? Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:02.60,Italics,Paula,0,0,0,,Well, since we're just getting started, \NI should probably take it easy—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:11.91,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.05,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Well, she's certainly fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.88,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,What in the world did Prontea teach her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:26.16,Italics,Ys,0,0,0,,Probably nothing in terms of combat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:29.84,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Well then, Ysley, let's see what you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:33.59,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,C-Certainly. \NPleasure to be working with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.61,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,You still alive, Paula?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:50.24,Italics,Ys,0,0,0,,Can't talk, huh? \NProbably a punctured lung, I'd wager.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:56.05,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I can't believe the dumb old bitch \Njust chucked me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.96,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,My face still smarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:02.74,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Ysley and Paula. \NWhat brings you guys around?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:05.08,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Finally decide to start training?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:09.18,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Oh, damn, is Paula almost dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:12.02,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,She won't be able to move \Nfor three days, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:14.43,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,You never hold back, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.54,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Well, don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:21.56,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,You get your organs mashed up enough, \Nyou stop worrying about it eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:26.00,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Okay, Hayato, we're sparring again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.81,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,What, already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:34.93,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Ysley, you're up again in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:40.85,Italics,Ys,0,0,0,,I hadn't abandoned my training\Nwith her previously just because it was harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:44.54,Italics,Ys,0,0,0,,I couldn't accept that this daily routine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:48.22,Italics,Ys,0,0,0,,would amount to any real growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:55.43,Flashback,Ys,0,0,0,,Why is it that we Idaten know our names \Nat the moment of our manifestation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.43,Flashback,Rin,0,0,0,,Couldn't say. It's a good question, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:01.12,Flashback,Ys,0,0,0,,How does the drawing out \Nprocess work, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:04.84,Flashback,Ys,0,0,0,,How exactly do we appear in nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:08.71,Flashback,Ys,0,0,0,,It should be impossible for organisms \Nto simply appear from nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:11.57,Flashback,Rin,0,0,0,,We're gods, so doesn't that explain it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:15.66,Flashback,Ys,0,0,0,,Then, as deities, why do we \Nhave human appearances,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:18.12,Flashback,Ys,0,0,0,,manifest wearing human clothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.44,Flashback,Ys,0,0,0,,and communicate with human language?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.04,Flashback,Rin,0,0,0,,No clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:28.28,Italics,Ys,0,0,0,,I also thought talking to her\N was a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:37.46,sign_13791_138_Zoble_Military_F,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1010,1)}Zoble Military\NFront Line
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:42.31,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,We are not waging a defensive war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.02,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,We espouse no lukewarm ideology, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.48,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,This is an invasion, plain and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.02,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,Now, tell me what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.42,Main,Soldiers,0,0,0,,We want to kill, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.71,Main,Soldiers,0,0,0,,We want to steal, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:53.10,Main,Soldiers,0,0,0,,We want to spoil, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:54.57,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,Who do you want to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:56.21,Main,Soldiers,0,0,0,,Our enemies, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.65,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,What do you want to steal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:59.11,Main,Soldiers,0,0,0,,Their wealth, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.70,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,And what do you want to spoil?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.73,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,The finest girl I can find, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:03.62,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Virgins, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:04.92,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Little girls, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:05.40,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,A housewife in front of her husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:06.40,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Shotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.45,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,A beefy older gent, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:09.53,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,{\an8}Too far, dude! Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:10.96,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,I respect your candor. Permission granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:15.46,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,The land and resources will belong to Zoble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.59,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,Everything else is your reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:22.30,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,Pillage to your heart's content, you dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:26.22,Main,Troops,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:28.36,Main,Messenger,0,0,0,,I have a report, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:32.51,Main,Messenger,0,0,0,,All C-Soldiers are to return \Nto base immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:35.40,Main,Messenger,0,0,0,,There was an emergency \Nnotification from Dr. Obami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.40,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,From the De... the doctor, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.81,Main,Messenger,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am. What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:43.79,Main,Messenger,0,0,0,,Requesting a return in the \Nmiddle of a battle like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:46.98,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'll be the only one returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:49.80,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,The outcome of this battle \Nwas a foregone conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:54.01,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,By the way, I'd take a few \Nsteps back if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.42,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,There's a missile headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:01.84,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,What... General?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.39,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:08.18,Main,Greens,0,0,0,,Direct hit confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.77,Main,Greens,0,0,0,,Did we take out General Piscalat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:19.16,Main,Greens,0,0,0,,Reload immediately! \NFire as soon as the target is—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.54,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,Idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:32.58,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,Ready a jet for me. \NI leave the rest in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:34.79,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,Take {\i1}everything{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:37.21,Main,Troops,0,0,0,,Ma'am! Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.65,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,All right, that should do for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:50.94,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:55.68,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Come on, guys. Let's go hang out. \NCan you move yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:57.32,Main,Sign/Spoken,0,0,0,,Dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.32,Main,Sign/Spoken,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs30\b1\bord0\shad1\c&HF11CC6&\4c&H821073&\frz20\pos(147.429,52.857)\fad(600,1)}D
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.32,Main,Sign/Spoken,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs30\b1\bord0\shad1\c&HF11CC6&\4c&H821073&\frz5\fad(600,1)\pos(241.715,58)}D
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.32,Main,Sign/Spoken,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs30\b1\bord0\shad1\c&HF11CC6&\4c&H821073&\frz5\fad(600,1)\pos(174.286,45.428)}E
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.32,Main,Sign/Spoken,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs30\b1\bord0\shad1\c&HF11CC6&\4c&H821073&\frz-15\fad(600,1)\pos(204.572,48.285)}A
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.21,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,Dying... Gonna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:03.57,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Paula, your eyes are doing \Nsome kinda fish thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:07.43,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,Ysley, is there really any \Npurpose to this training?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:09.69,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's not just torture?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:13.58,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,I wondered the same thing for a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:17.54,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,But there is a proper logic to it,\N so rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:20.61,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,What the hell's logic \Ngot to do with training?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:23.46,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,You fight every day, \Nyou're bound to get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:28.71,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Honestly, I envy your \Nsimplistic outlook, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:31.29,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Wouldn't most people\Nturn to weight training instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:35.14,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,That said, weight training \Nwould be pointless for Idaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:38.44,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Since we've got nothing to do until \Nwe're healed, I might as well explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:41.69,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Don't care. Your explanations \Nare too confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:45.34,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.45,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Did you have to make it sound so pitiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:48.95,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.11,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,We Idaten are different on a\N cellular level from all other organisms,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:49.95,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:51.03,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,including humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:50.95,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:52.05,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Hence the unique training.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:51.95,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:53.44,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Consider how we can survive \Nhaving our hearts crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:52.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.50,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Rin-san believes our \Nsupernatural nature explains this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:53.96,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:54.96,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.33,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,but demons die easily when \N{\i1}their{\i0} hearts are crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:55.96,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.46,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,See, the destruction of the heart \Nstops the circulatory system,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:56.96,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:57.96,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:12:59.77,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,halting the delivery of oxygen and nutrients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:12:58.96,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:12:59.96,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.40,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,This is where we differ from living creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:00.96,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.37,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,We require no nutrition\N and don't really need to breathe,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:01.96,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:02.96,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.51,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,thus a lack of circulating \Nblood is no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:03.97,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:04.97,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.96,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Though we act short of breath when tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:05.97,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:07.12,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,this is more a "habit" than anything else—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:06.97,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:07.82,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,a habit of living creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:07.97,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:08.85,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Our genesis lies in the \Nthoughts of living creatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:08.97,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:09.94,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,and our creation is dictated by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:09.97,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.50,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,The reason we have human forms\N rather than anything else
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:10.97,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:11.97,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.13,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,is that humans have considerably\Nmore thoughts than other creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:12.97,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:15.16,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,The reason you specifically are able \Nto speak with birds is because
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:13.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:14.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:16.16,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,you're partly composed of bird thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:15.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:16.76,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Now then,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:16.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.38,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,what does any of this have to do\N with torturous training?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:17.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.48,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,Hayato was actually right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:18.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:20.77,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,The more your organs are destroyed,\N the less it bothers you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:19.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:20.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.32,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,His body is already become\Nsomething distinctly inhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:21.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.89,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,In exchange, he's gained something\Nthat living creatures do not have:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:22.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:23.99,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:25.86,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,a metamorphosis which makes \Nhim more effective in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:24.99,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:25.99,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:27.80,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,The kind of evolution we undergo\N is tied to our own thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:26.99,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}Fast Forward Explanation in Progress
